  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment (Minimal Profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct. COU1 is the validation activity itself — the FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two laboratories. All 13 V&V 40 factors assessed; one factor (Test conditions) below required level due to single test condition. This model has been applied in clinical research settings to support pre-market submissions and post-market surveillance activities for spinal fixation devices, providing biomechanical performance predictions under quasi-static loading.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/nagaraja-f1717-compression-bending-req",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/nagaraja-fea-compression-bending-claim",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/synth/model/nagaraja-pedicle-screw-fea-ensemble",
